    <title>Contacts</title>
</head>
<body>
    <button id="home">HOME</button>
    <div class="contacts">
        <h1>Contact Kwadabuka Poultry Farm</h1>

        <p>Get in touch with us for fresh, high-quality chicken. We breed and feed our 
           chickens with care, offering both slaughtered (dressed) and unslaughterd (live) 
           options to suit your needs.
        </p>

        <h1>Order Details</h1>

        <ul>
            <li>Service Options: Convenient farm pickup or fast delivery straight to your doorstep.</li>
            <li>Order Types: Available in bulk or individual purchases.</li>
        </ul>

        <h1>Our Contact Information</h1>

        <ul>
            <li>📞 Cell Phone: 0742464777</li>
            <li>✉️ Email: Kwadabuka@gmail.com</li>
            <li>📍 Location: KwaDabuka</li>
        </ul>

        <h1>Operating Hours</h1>

        <ul>
            <li>Monday to Saturday: 08:00 AM – 05:00 PM</li>
            <li>Sunday: Closed</li>
        </ul>

        <div>
            <h1>Send Us a Message</h1>

            <p>Have a question or want to place a bulk order? Fill out the form below, and our team will 
                get back to you as soon as possible.
            </p>

            <form action="">
            
                <ul>

                    <li>
                        <label for="name">Name</label>
                        <input type="text" name="name">
                    </li><br>
                    
                    <li>
                        <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
                        <input type="text" name="phone">
                    </li>

                    <li>
                        <h1>Your Order / Inquiry:</h1>
                        
                        <label for="unsltd">Unslaughtered</label>
                        <input type="checkbox" name="unsltd" id="">

                        <label for="sltd">Slaughtered</label>
                        <input type="checkbox" name="sltd" id="">
                    </li><br>

                    <li>
                        <label for="massage">Massage</label>
                        input <textarea name="massage" id=""></textarea>
                    </li>

                </ul>

                <button>Send </button>

            </form>

        </div>

        


